е“°зЁ®Е’дҹЈеҹӮгҺ«д¬•еҮҲжҮҚдҮӣеҹ¬еҚ–бЁҡаҜӘзЈҗвіҲдӢ°еЁҪе•ҙеӢ–гҖ дқӮаөөдЎәеқ•а«“е–ҳеҖ¬!Х°гҡҘдӯ®дҚөгёҗбҲ«дӮҠд°®ж…Ёбј©дҲҺзө№жӘ¶зӢӮе®ғбҙҸбӮ¬в—…бӨ»гғ°гЎ…гҰ№г—®ж№ӯв„ҲМ В…дө©жҜ”жҝҚЛҠеҘ ВіеЎҗЦ JдҠёеҮҫдӘӨе””жҠ”дҶіаӘ…дғқе°өбҗҖзӘ‘з”   \"}]"},"redirectURL":"","headersSize":253,"bodySize":1272,"_status":"completed","_startTimestamp":1775056049428533,"_endTimestamp":1775056049433580},"cache":{},"timings":{"send":-1,"wait":-1,"receive":-1},"serverIPAddress":"47.252.2.215","connection":"92","comment":"","_id":1103,"_uid":"9b614801-c7a7-428b-992f-fecfeb6a2ef2","_cid":92,"_ctime":1775055887626,"_sid":62,"_stime":1775056046512,"_serverAddress":"47.252.2.215","_serverAddressFamily":0,"_serverPort":9300,"_clientAddress":"127.0.0.1","_clientAddressFamily":0,"_clientPort":41326,"_app":{"name":"Legend of the Cosmic Warriors","id":"com.cosmicwartwn.the"}},{"startedDateTime":"2026-04-01T15:07:26.190Z","time":284,"request":{"method":"GET","url":"https://s398-zd.pksilo.com:9300/socket.io/?EIO=3&transport=polling&t=Pr9bSXb&sid=ZIFlnwc_Kqme9OHHAAmW","httpVersion":"HTTP/1.1","cookies":[],"headers":[{"name":"Host","value":"s398-zd.pksilo.com:9300"},{"name":"Accept-Encoding","value":"deflate, gzip"},{"name":"User-Agent","value":"Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 12; itel S665L Build/SP1A.210812.016) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/61.0.2883.95 Mobile Safari/537.36 EgretNative"},{"name":"Accept","value":"*/*"}],"queryString":[{"name":"EIO","value":"3"},{"name":"transport","value":"polling"},{"name":"t","value":"Pr9bSXb"},{"name":"sid","value":"ZIFlnwc_Kqme9OHHAAmW"}],"headersSize":247,"bodySize":0,"_status":"completed","_startTimestamp":1775056046190558,"_endTimestamp":1775056046197110},"response":{"status":200,"statusText":"OK","httpVersion":"HTTP/1.1","cookies":[{"name":"io","value":"ZIFlnwc_Kqme9OHHAAmW"}],"headers":[{"name":"Server","value":"nginx"},{"name":"Date","value":"Wed, 01 Apr 2026 15:07:27 GMT"},{"name":"Content-Type","value":"text/plain; charset=UTF-8"},{"name":"Content-Length","